Hashtable的hash碰撞</p>","keywords":null,"cover":"/image/cc71.png","content":null,"text":"java_cc链7cc链7依旧是触发LazyMap的get方法的另一种思路，主要是采用Hashtable的hash碰撞环境apache commons collection3.1-3.2.1jdk1.7，1.8调用栈1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"java_cc链6","slug":"java-cc链6","date":"2023-07-19T09:39:13.000Z","updated":"2023-07-19T09:39:47.274Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/java-cc链6.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"java-cc链6\"><a href=\"#java-cc链6\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"java_cc链6\"></a>java_cc链6</h1><p>这是一条除BadAttributeValueExpException以外调用LazyMa.get方法的链子，也就是cc链5的变形</p>","keywords":null,"cover":"/image/cc61.png","content":null,"text":"java_cc链6这是一条除BadAttributeValueExpException以外调用LazyMa.get方法的链子，也就是cc链5的变形环境apache commons collection3.1-3.2.1jdk1.7，1.8调用链1<br>2<br>3<br>4<b","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"java_cc链5","slug":"java-cc链5","date":"2023-07-19T09:38:24.000Z","updated":"2023-07-19T09:38:51.103Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/java-cc链5.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"java-cc链5\"><a href=\"#java-cc链5\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"java_cc链5\"></a>java_cc链5</h1><p>这里我们又回到了去触发 LazyMap.get()，只不过我们改变了 LazyMap.get() 的触发方式，不再和 CC1 和 CC3 一样借助 AnnotationInvocationHandler 的反序列化触发。</p>","keywords":null,"cover":"/image/cc51.png","content":null,"text":"java_cc链5这里我们又回到了去触发 LazyMap.get()，只不过我们改变了 LazyMap.get() 的触发方式，不再和 CC1 和 CC3 一样借助 AnnotationInvocationHandler 的反序列化触发。环境apache commons coll","link":"","raw":null,"photos":[],"categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"java_cc链4","slug":"java-cc链4","date":"2023-07-19T09:37:27.000Z","updated":"2023-07-19T09:38:17.214Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/java-cc链4.json","excerpt":"<h1 id=\"java-cc链4\"><a href=\"#java-cc链4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"java_cc链4\"></a>java_cc链4</h1><p>上面 CC2 说了因为 CommonsCollections4 除4.0的其他版本去掉了 InvokerTransformer 的 Serializable 继承，导致无法序列化。所以我们是否可以不使用 InvokerTransformer 呢？于是便有了 CC4，其实cc链4就是cc2链中In